    <item>
      <title>Trans VRMMO But I Suck At Videogames</title>
      <author> naomeatmybutt </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1359123/trans-vrmmo-but-i-suck-at-videogames/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1359123-trans-vrmmo-but-i-suck-at-videogames/chapter/1359125/#comments</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">16ad276329d78b1e63dd63533d5759e20c625095</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This new VRMMO looks cool, I probably don't need the tutorial though. Just let me make my usual pretty character and play already, god.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1359123-trans-vrmmo-but-i-suck-at-videogames/chapter/1359125/"&gt;&lt;div class="chapter-title"&gt;Gored&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="chp_raw" id="chp_raw"&gt;&lt;p&gt;“And&lt;em&gt; that&lt;/em&gt; is how you add a template to your slideshow. Finish up your projects by Tuesday, and I’ll see you soon.” &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;While you might think this is a class for sixth graders, it’s actually the sound of a mandatory Bimbleton Community College prerequisite course. Nothing better than paying hundreds of dollars for an old lady to teach adults how to make a slideshow. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;At least our presentations can be about whatever we want. Mine’s focused on that time Loki turned into a girl horse to do epic pranks. I’ve always liked that story for some reason, surely it won’t be awkward to discuss with my peers.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I say peers since I’ve been going here for over a year now and still haven’t really made any friends. There’s one dude in storyboarding who seems cool, but every time I try and speak up, I get lightheaded and need to sit down. Last week I tried bringing up D&amp;amp;D after he mentioned it in class and I had a legitimate panic attack. God I’m pathetic.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;It’s not that I’m an introvert or anything, I love spending time with people. I just feel so disconnected from them all the time, like why would anyone want to talk to a giant, lanky weirdo who looks like Shrek fucked Slenderman?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;At least I have something to look forward to this weekend. &lt;b&gt;The appropriately titled &lt;em&gt;GAME NAME&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/b&gt; just dropped, a full dive VRMMO that swears it’s not gonna kill anyone this time. One benefit of living in bumfuck nowhere with molasses internet is that I had to queue up the download two days ago, so hopefully some of the launch issues have been addressed by now.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Arriving home after my short 40 minute commute, I see mom sitting at the kitchen table glaring at her laptop. We briefly exchange emotionless pleasantries without making eye contact as I run upstairs to sequester myself in my room. I’d lock the door but for some reason I got the only room without a lock. Super fun when your parents barge in on you in the middle of trying on &lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;HEY&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; look at that the download finished!&lt;i&gt;  &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I don my headset and lay back in my far too tiny bed, thankful for the distraction as studio logos encompass my view.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;hr /&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Navigating to the &lt;em&gt;&lt;b&gt;GAME NAME&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/em&gt; tab, the game boots with forty seconds of flashing disclaimers telling epileptics to fuck off. Honestly the worst thing about VR is not having a skip cutscene button to mash over and over. Also all those kids who died I guess.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I quickly find myself in a see through box in the sky, overlooking a picturesque planet below me. A non-diegetic title card appears to fanfare while one stoked dude proclaims "&lt;em&gt;&lt;b&gt;GAMEEEE NAMEEEE" &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/em&gt;like it’s an SNL musical guest.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Landing on the &lt;i&gt;create character &lt;/i&gt;option, I begin scrolling through classes. Barbarian, Monk, Wizard, huh these are pretty bog standard. Figured there’d be some cool spellblade magic punch slam dunkster or something. Fucking WoW clones. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I settle on Cleric because I want people to like me and need as little stress as possible. Besides, how hard could it be to not fuck up healing?&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The stat array popped up with your usual six descriptors. I debated looking up build guides, but honestly at this point I really just wanted to get into the game. So I pumped everything into Dex &amp;amp; Wis, leaving Str, Con, Chr &amp;amp; Int as dump stats. Presumably that will let my ADHD brain be fast and do cleric stuff; it’ll be a cold day in hell when I invest a single point into Defense. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;From there I’m thrust into the intricate skill system tutorial. &lt;i&gt;The skill system allows you to slot in specific subskills and subskill gems into primary fused skills to create an endless supply of&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;fuck this I’m bored. Select defaults &amp;amp; Skip.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Another menu UGH why do games do this? Oh thank god it’s just appearance customization, the part I actually like.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I always like playing as a girl in games when given the opportunity. My friends have asked me about it before and I have plenty of legitimate reasons I definitely didn’t rehearse ahead of time involving looking at asses or treating it the same as if I were playing a Mermaid or something for the novelty of an imaginary mythical thing that could never really happen haha.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I mess with presets making my usual: a pale, befreckled redhead with winged eyeliner, a nose stud and matte black lipstick. I always figured if I was a girl that’s how I’d like to look, plus picturing playing as the default Geralt ass buff dude makes me physically ill.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I spend a while futsing with intricate jaw height &amp;amp; eye distance sliders before zooming out to witness my deformed mutant and resetting to a slightly modified default. Thank god I’ll never have to worry about putting a real woman’s face together.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I name her Blarblegarble so I can play it off as a joke character if I run into anyone I know. I called my Pokemon Emerald character Erin as a kid for whatever reason and got so much shit for it despite how weirdly happy it made me.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Finishing up by randomly selecting pregenerated backstory details &lt;i&gt;oh my god let me innnnnnnn&lt;/i&gt;, I select a server and fall into it.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Literally, the glass box falls away at my feet and I plummet to the ground below.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;hr /&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Soaring through the sky in VR is a trip. Feeling the tingling chill on my hands and the wind coursing through my hair is incredible and makes me wish I never had to buzz the beautiful shaggy mess my shop teacher ever so kindly referred to as girl hair.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As I rapidly approach terminal velocity, I find that I’m able to subtly angle my meatsack to direct where I land. My options appear to be a small village or creepy forest. Knowing myself, I determine if I’m exposed to any more boring exposition I’m liable to commit war crimes, so forest it is.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Crashing through the canopy, I somehow land without splatting and emerge with only a handful of severe gashes etched into my skin.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Huh, speaking of, my body feels really good. A little iron deficient maybe but that’s nothing new. I grab my arms and &lt;i&gt;holy shit &lt;/i&gt;my skin is so smooth when it's not being scraped off at high speeds.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I lay there massaging myself for an embarrassingly long time before hearing the huff of a frenzied wild boar sizing me up from six feet away. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Now I want you to picture fighting a wild boar as yourself. No fancy magic or gear, just barehanded man vs. beast. Don’t know about ya’ll, but I’m 99% sure I’d get my ass gored.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The boar charges and by some miracle I tumble to the side just in time to keep my liver inside. Thank god for dexterity. I pause a moment to open the menu and check my &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;FUCK&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Ow, make that 100%. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Ok so you can’t pause mid game. Duh, it’s an MMO, not sure why I was thinking like my mom. No wonder she calls me hopeless.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You'd Never guess but having no Con score and wearing nothing but a short travelling dress means being gored by a wild boar &lt;i&gt;hurts.&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Wait, I’m in a dress?!? Holy shit. I’m not sure if it’s the blood loss or what but I feel giddy. I mean I used to try on my sister’s clothes all the time when they were gone before dad found out and &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;FUCK&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Oh yeah, boar. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;My consciousness fades as I realize I just died to a &lt;i&gt;boar in the starting area. &lt;/i&gt;God I suck.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I float there in third person desaturated purgatory waiting for the respawn timer, and let me tell you seeing your own dead body is a trip.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;I figured I’d be dissociating like a ghost, but I feel weirdly drawn to it. Something about those emerald eyes staring into the abyss makes me feel more connected to that body than I ever did my own. Suddenly, the sight of Babe tearing into its chest feels wrong. What kind of asshole takes a defenseless girl and hurts her like that? &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As the clock ticks down, I acknowledge that dying kinda sucks, but at least I respawn nearby. Very nearby. Like 20 feet away nearby. I’m close enough that I can still see the gore splattered pig chomping into a very pretty corpse. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Wait, am I pretty? &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Sssssh brain, backburner. I’m getting the drop on that dickhead this time.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Sneaking through the brush towards the boar, I start chanting what I think is a basic spell and &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;OW, FUCK, SECOND BOAR.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="wi_authornotes"&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;div class="p-avatar-wrap"&gt;&lt;a class="avatar has-link" href="/profile/185197/naomeatmybutt/"&gt;&lt;img id="acc_ava_change profile" alt="" src="https://cdn.scribblehub.com/avatar/s/46/ava_185197_1735099896.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="an_username"&gt;&lt;a href="/profile/185197/naomeatmybutt/"&gt;naomeatmybutt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div style="clear: both;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="wi_authornotes_body"&gt;  First time writing something with an actual narrative, figured I'd start by poking fun at a genre I read way too much of :) &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
